{"tid":2087243,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發！攬炒團隊 x Hong Kong Watch成功推動 「歐洲議會關注香港小組」成立】","createTime":"2020-06-30T15:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T12:28:11.000Z","uid":205927,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e882b0e2f7f8e890e69dfa1c694807a3fcdf52f4","tid":2087243,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"【突發！攬炒團隊 x Hong Kong Watch成功推動 「歐洲議會關注香港小組」成立】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共強行通過國安法，瞬間摧毀各個抗爭組織。喺手足歸隊前，攬炒團隊點都會盡力奮戰到底。<br />\n<br />\n過去半年，我地團隊、歐洲各國手足（尤其Hong Kong Watch）等不斷努力破局，除咗上星期大比數通過支持香港議案；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*謹此*<br />\n宣布「歐洲議會關注香港小組」正式成立！<br />\n<br />\n我地有幸邀請到5位議員(MEP)聯合出任小組主席，同時正式邀請各國議員加入！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，我地以舊年推動成立「英國國會跨黨派香港小組」方式喺歐盟破局，盡力：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 推動歐盟恆常討論、跟進香港局勢<br />\n(2) 凝聚一班固定支持香港嘅歐洲議會議員<br />\n(3) 協調歐洲跨黨派支持香港後續行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主席(排名不分先後):<br />\n- Reinhard Buetikofer MEP (Greens-EFA/ Germany)<br />\n- Miriam Lexmann MEP (EPP/ Slovakia)<br />\n- Petras Austrevicius MEP (Renew Europe/ Lithuania)<br />\n- Anna Fotyga MEP (ECR/ Poland)<br />\n- Juan Fernando Aguilar Lopez MEP (S&amp;D/ Spain)<br />\n<br />\n小組成員：<br />\n- 7月1日開始邀請全體MEP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑暗時期下，更加要努力反勝。<br />\n希望手足盡力鼓勵歐洲各國MEP加入香港小組，重光之路永不滅！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n攬炒團隊《重光計劃》眾籌突破85%🔥<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gofundme.com/f/swhk-fundraiser\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fswhk-fundraiser&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=88e07e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.gofundme.com/f/swhk-fundraiser</a><br />\n<br />\n正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8c29085f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/StirFryChannel</a>"},{"pid":"5083641e87e29a71cad15a19262490b05abfd48b","tid":2087243,"uid":41610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"c4c3cdf0c8775f05730d8cbbdca24bbdb3a7b97a","tid":2087243,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a500cca57b700aa50ab727540fe91aeea31197","tid":2087243,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f61b11dde8f8816a6e516d18a747dbf1d598a1","tid":2087243,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5083641e87e29a71cad15a19262490b05abfd48b","tid":2087243,"uid":41610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"71見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGyk19q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGyk19q.jpg&h=621aff59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouv7G9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fouv7G9r.jpg&h=f28bc6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XhWnv2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhWnv2N.jpg&h=98daaba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkU4KnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkU4KnP.jpg&h=d17116aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https: